(startRule compilationUnit M-ID .  TERMINATESTMT .\n       \n       \n        FILE-CONTROL .\n           SELECT SOMEFILE1 ASSIGN TO 'somefile1.txt' .\n        IVISION .\n       \n        FD SOMEFILE1 .\n           01 ITEMS .\n        URE DIVISION .\n       \n        FROM SOMEID1 BEFORE ADVANCING 3 LINES AT EOP DISPLAY 'at end of page' NOT AT EOP DISPLAY 'not at end of page' INVALID KEY DISPLAY 'invalid key' NOT INVALID KEY DISPLAY 'valid key' .)